::Cerberus/Four Nightmares/Nemean Hydra::

    "Destrons," Cerberus said. "We still haven't salvaged the Destron 
base, that is my number one priority. I would hope it would be the 
same as yours. I am going to go back and start. Once I am finished."
    He looked around at all the bots. "We will come back and help 
these 'Transformers' if we can."
    He turned and left with the Four Nightmares and Nemean Hydra. He 
hoped the others would follow.
